  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"spell-description\">\n  <p>\n    <strong>School</strong>&nbsp;transmutation&nbsp;[evil];\n    <strong>Level</strong>&nbsp;antipaladin 3;\n    \n    \n    \n    \n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Casting Time</strong>&nbsp;1 standard action<br>\n    <strong>Components</strong>&nbsp;V, S<br>\n  </p>\n  <p>\n    <strong>Range</strong>&nbsp;touch<br>\n    \n    <strong>Targets</strong>&nbsp;your fiendish boon weapon<br>\n    \n    <strong>Duration</strong>&nbsp;1 minute/level<br>\n    <strong>Saving Throw</strong>&nbsp;Will negates (harmless);&nbsp;<strong>Spell Resistance</strong>&nbsp;no<br>\n  </p>\n  <h2>Description</h2>\n  <p>You strengthen the bond between your fiendish boon weapon and its unholy spirit. The weapon gains the <i>ghost touch</i> property.</p><p>You may change your weapon's damage type (bludgeoning, piercing, slashing) as a swift action. You gain a profane bonus to your CMD against disarm and sunder attacks directed at your boon weapon; this bonus is equal to half your caster level.</p>\n</div>\n",
